casebody.data:
Eric E. JOHNSON, petitioner,
v.
Ralph DIAZ, Acting Secretary, California Department of Corrections and Rehabilitation. No. 18-5645. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 29, 2018.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States *447Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
